data.description: New! This turnkey 2-bedroom 1.5-bathroom home features new laminate flooring, new interior paint, new fireplace, new entry hallway lights, new patio cover, new shelves, new ceiling fan, new bathroom sinks, new toilet, new baseboards, new bathroom sliding glass doors, new smoke alarms, new ring camera, and a new hot water heater! This unit is extremely rare since it comes with A/C! $3K credit to buyer with seller's preferred lender. Call listing agent for details. Condo is centrally located and walking distance to shopping, parks, schools, and freeways. It has one entrance next to the large common area lawn and the back entrance next to the carport and patio. The patio is fully fenced and covered. It comes with a covered carport and an uncovered parking space along with additional parking for guests.
